oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Quentin Rankin and Robert Z. Taylor
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two images of two different men, Captain Quentin Rankin, in glasses and military uniform, and Colonel Robert Z. Taylor, in a suit with tie. Both were targets of violence by Night Riders in 1908 at Reelfoot Lake in Lake County, Tennessee. Part of a series of Reelfoot night rider images.
